subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: In the Women’s N.C.A.A. tournament, the unbeaten Huskies showed they were as sharp as ever; the Terrapins extended their winning streak to 13 games; and the Blue Devils built on an early 11-0 run.
